revisions.description: updated comments, use FlowActivityState instead of CadMapStatsGreedyId, rename cadMapStatsTotalGrantPendingTooLongDrops

cadMapStatsMib.contactinfo: Arris Technical Support Postal: ARRIS Phone: +1 770 622 8530 E-Mail: support@arrisi.com
cadMapStatsMib.description: This MIB contains objects to display counts and statistical information for the DOCSIS map-makers. There exists a single map-maker for each upstream channel. The map-makers hold the keys to the upstream bandwidth. Thus, one is able to gain insight into how the upstream bandwidth is being managed by analyzing the various map-maker counts and statistics in this MIB.

CadMapStatsIUCTypeId.name: CadMapStatsIUCTypeId
CadMapStatsIUCTypeId.description: Interval Usage Code, a field in MAP and UCD messages which link burst profiles to grants.

cadMapStatsTotalMapsSent.name: cadMapStatsTotalMapsSent
cadMapStatsTotalMapsSent.description: Total number of maps transmitted downstream for this UChannel.

cadMapStatsTotalFragmentedGrants.name: cadMapStatsTotalFragmentedGrants
cadMapStatsTotalFragmentedGrants.description: Total number of fragmented bandwidth grants for this UChannel.

cadMapStatsTotalUgsQiTransitions.name: cadMapStatsTotalUgsQiTransitions
cadMapStatsTotalUgsQiTransitions.description: Total number of UGS QI transitions. Useful for debugging VoIP.

cadMapStatsTotalUgsadTransitions.name: cadMapStatsTotalUgsadTransitions
cadMapStatsTotalUgsadTransitions.description: Total number of UGSAD flow transitions. Useful for debugging VoIP.

cadMapStatsTotalUgsEHdrsSw.name: cadMapStatsTotalUgsEHdrsSw
cadMapStatsTotalUgsEHdrsSw.description: Total number of UGS Service Flow Extended Headers processed in software. Useful for debugging VoIP.

cadMapStatsTotalBadMaps.name: cadMapStatsTotalBadMaps
cadMapStatsTotalBadMaps.description: Total number of maps discarded due to errors for this UChannel

cadMapStatsTotalMSlots.name: cadMapStatsTotalMSlots
cadMapStatsTotalMSlots.description: Total Minislots count for this UChannel.

cadMapStatsTotalUCastGrantedMSlots.name: cadMapStatsTotalUCastGrantedMSlots
cadMapStatsTotalUCastGrantedMSlots.description: Total Minislots granted to Unicast for this UChannel.

cadMapStatsTotalBwRequestMSlots.name: cadMapStatsTotalBwRequestMSlots
cadMapStatsTotalBwRequestMSlots.description: Total Minislots requested via bandwidth requests for this UChannel. This count does not include requests dropped due to SuperGreedy in hardware.

cadMapStatsTotalSkippedMSlots.name: cadMapStatsTotalSkippedMSlots
cadMapStatsTotalSkippedMSlots.description: Total Minislots not granted because the MapMaker was behind.

cadMapStatsTotalLogicalNullPadMSlots.name: cadMapStatsTotalLogicalNullPadMSlots
cadMapStatsTotalLogicalNullPadMSlots.description: Total Minislots allocated to the NULL SID for a logical channel which is inactive

cadMapStatsGrantedBCastMSlots.name: cadMapStatsGrantedBCastMSlots
cadMapStatsGrantedBCastMSlots.description: For each IUC type, the total number of minislots granted to the Broadcast SID.

cadMapStatsGrantedMCastMSlots.name: cadMapStatsGrantedMCastMSlots
cadMapStatsGrantedMCastMSlots.description: For each IUC type, the total number of minislots granted to Multicast SIDs.

cadMapStatsGrantedUCastMSlots.name: cadMapStatsGrantedUCastMSlots
cadMapStatsGrantedUCastMSlots.description: For each IUC type, the total number of minislots granted to Unicast SIDs.

cadMapStatsGrantedZeroSidMSlots.name: cadMapStatsGrantedZeroSidMSlots
cadMapStatsGrantedZeroSidMSlots.description: For each IUC type, the total number of minislots granted to the Zero SID.

cadMapStatsTotalBwRequests.name: cadMapStatsTotalBwRequests
cadMapStatsTotalBwRequests.description: Total number of Bandwidth Requests processed for this UChannel. This count does not include requests dropped due to SuperGreedy in hardware.

cadMapStatsTotalBwRequestSchedulerDrops.name: cadMapStatsTotalBwRequestSchedulerDrops
cadMapStatsTotalBwRequestSchedulerDrops.description: Total number of Bandwidth Requests dropped by the MapMaker without giving a grant or grant pending. This count does not include grant pending drops.

cadMapStatsTotalBwRequestSuperGreedyDrop.name: cadMapStatsTotalBwRequestSuperGreedyDrops
cadMapStatsTotalBwRequestSuperGreedyDrop.description: Total number of Bandwidth Requests dropped due to the service flow being in the super greedy state. This should not happen if the cable modem is properly policing its service flows.

cadMapStatsPeakBwRequestSize.name: cadMapStatsPeakBwRequestSize
cadMapStatsPeakBwRequestSize.description: The peak size of a Bandwidth request received since the last read.

cadMapStatsPeakBwRequestsPerMap.name: cadMapStatsPeakBwRequestsPerMap
cadMapStatsPeakBwRequestsPerMap.description: The peak number of Bandwidth requests per map received since the last read.

cadMapStatsTotalGrantPendings.name: cadMapStatsTotalGrantPendings
cadMapStatsTotalGrantPendings.description: Total number of Grant Pendings given for this UChannel.

cadMapStatsTotalGrantPendingDrops.name: cadMapStatsTotalGrantPendingDrops
cadMapStatsTotalGrantPendingDrops.description: Total number of Grant Pendings Dropped by the MapMaker for this UChannel. These are dropped primarily for pending for too long or too many grants pending per map.

cadMapStatsTotalGrantPendingPromos.name: cadMapStatsTotalGrantPendingPromos
cadMapStatsTotalGrantPendingPromos.description: Total number of Grant Pendings Promoted by the MapMaker to a higher priority (less greedy) queue for this UChannel.

cadMapStatsPeakGrantPendingsPerMap.name: cadMapStatsPeakGrantPendingsPerMap
cadMapStatsPeakGrantPendingsPerMap.description: The peak number of Bandwidth requests per map received since the last read.

cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesNumAdds.name: cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesNumAdds
cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesNumAdds.description: For each Bandwidth Request priority Queue, the total number of bandwidth requests added to this queue. This includes requests promoted from lower priority queues.

cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesNumDrops.name: cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesNumDrops
cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesNumDrops.description: For each Bandwidth Request priority Queue, the total number of requests dropped. These are dropped primarily for pending for too long or too many grants pending per map.

cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesNumPendings.name: cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesNumPendings
cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesNumPendings.description: For each Bandwidth Request priority Queue, the total number of grant pendings given to bandwidth requests on this queue.

cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesNumPromos.name: cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesNumPromos
cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesNumPromos.description: For each Bandwidth Request priority Queue, the total number of bandwidth requests promoted from this queue to a higher priority (less greedy) queue.

cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesNumElements.name: cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesNumElements
cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesNumElements.description: For each Bandwidth Request priority Queue, the current number of bandwidth requests in the queue.

cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesLatencySum.name: cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesLatencySum
cadMapStatsBwRequestQueuesLatencySum.description: For each Bandwidth Request priority Queue, the sum of the latency in usecs for each bandwidth request from receive time to grant or drop time. Latency for requests which are promoted is counted in the promoted to queue.

cadMapStatsNumNrtpsFlows.name: cadMapStatsNumNrtpsFlows
cadMapStatsNumNrtpsFlows.description: Current number of scheduled NRTPS flows for this UChannel.

cadMapStatsNumRtpsFlows.name: cadMapStatsNumRtpsFlows
cadMapStatsNumRtpsFlows.description: Current number of scheduled RTPS flows scheduled for this UChannel.

cadMapStatsNumUgsadActiveFlows.name: cadMapStatsNumUgsadActiveFlows
cadMapStatsNumUgsadActiveFlows.description: Current number of scheduled UGSAD flows in the Active (UGS) mode for this UChannel.

cadMapStatsNumUgsadPollingFlows.name: cadMapStatsNumUgsadPollingFlows
cadMapStatsNumUgsadPollingFlows.description: Current number of scheduled UGSAD flows in the Polling (RTPS) mode for this UChannel.

cadMapStatsNumUgsFlows.name: cadMapStatsNumUgsFlows
cadMapStatsNumUgsFlows.description: Current number of scheduled UGS flows for this UChannel.

cadMapStatsNumBEPollingFlows.name: cadMapStatsNumBEPollingFlows
cadMapStatsNumBEPollingFlows.description: Current number of scheduled Best Effort Polling flows for this UChannel. These are NRTPS request opportunities given to Best Effort flows based on the flow priority and guaranteed minimum reserved rate. This includes flows using both the fast and slow polling intervals.

cadMapStatsNumBEFastPollingFlows.name: cadMapStatsNumBEFastPollingFlows
cadMapStatsNumBEFastPollingFlows.description: Current number of scheduled Best Effort Fast Polling flows for this UChannel.
